title: Physical Goals at 90 Years Old
content: Envision yourself at 90 years old. What do you want to be able to do, physically? Perhaps it’s as simple as walking up two flights of stairs or playing on the floor with your great-grandkids.

title: Backcasting
content: In my practice, we call this backcasting, or reverse-engineering. We break down and train the movements of everyday life, outlining how “good” you need to be today to achieve your goals tomorrow.
